  B: Sian-siN, goa2 khi3 hoe2-chhia thau5 mng7, ia7 u7 khi3 phai3 chhut sou2 mng7, bo5 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3, u7 hit khoan2 gin2-na2, kau3 beh tng2-lai5 ti7 oat-kak hit keng be7 toa7-beh8 moai5 hia chiah mng7 tioh8 kong2 u7. 
