  I: TaN lai5 chhiaN2 li2 kong2 chit e5 gin2-a2 e5 tai7-chi3 hou7 goan2 thiaN hoN3. 
  P: To Jin5-ai3-a3 chhoa7 chit8-e5 gin2-a2 lai5, seng-khu ko7 kah choan5 thou5, khau3-kah bo5 siaN, te2 toa7-beh8-moai5 hou7 chiah8, ka7 mng7 koe3-lai5 mng7 koe3-khi3 ia7 long2 m7-in3. 
