  I: Si7, taN bo5 iau3-kin2, kah lang5 iau2 ti7-teh, kin2-ban7 e7 hou7 lan2 chhoe7-tioh8, chit tiong-kan chiah lai5 lian5-lok8, hit-e5 lang5 na7 u7 koh lai5 Ka-gi7, chhiaN2 li2 chiah po3 goa2 chai. 
